              GadFly: Genome Annotation Database of Drosophila
     __________________________________________________________________

   [bullet.gif] Query GadFly
   A fill-in-the-blank form for locating predicted genes
   [bullet.gif] ArmView2
   Interactive GIF display to browse genomic sequence maps by chromosome
   arm
   [bullet.gif] GeneSeen
   Interactive Java applet for graphical browsing of annotations
   [bullet.gif] Gene Ontology (GO) Browser
   Search ontology terms
   [bullet.gif] Map Position
   Predicted genes organized by chromosomal location
   [bullet.gif] Sequence Similarity Groups
   Predicted genes grouped on the basis of sequence similarities found
   between them
   [bullet.gif] Protein Domain
   Predicted proteins grouped by InterPro domain by EBI
   [bullet.gif] Drosophila Genomic Sequence Databases
   [bullet.gif] Fly BLAST
   Sequence similarity searching of Drosophila-specific datasets--results
   hyperlink to our database reports.

